commit.title: Micromega: updated CHANGES and bug fixes
commit.message:
Micromega: updated CHANGES and bug fixes

- CHANGES: advertise the Simplex solver and the Simplex option

- fix the generation of cutting planes (was not using the right proof
environment)

- fix a typo in Monomial.sqrt (was generating invalid proofs)
